In the Upper Palatinate and Upper Franconia, for example, there is no such thing in government residences.
In Swabia, too, single women refugees are not housed separately, says Karl-Heinz Meyer, a government spokesman.
In Upper Bavaria, Lower and Middle Franconia, some communal housing houses have floors or private houses for single women and their children only.
