How do sleep problems or sleep disorders manifest themselves?
There are several forms of sleep disorders, and they can have a variety of causes, emphasizes Hans- Günter Weeß, a board member of the German Society for Sleep Research and Sleep Medicine.
But what is commonly understood is insomnia, a sleep disorder.
